# Assets

- Prefer SF Symbols; prefix custom assets consistently.

# Strings

- Keep `Localizable.strings` organized; no hard-coded user-facing strings in code.

# Configuration

- Do not commit secrets. Use environment-specific configuration; document values during implementation (rule only).
